# Summer Analytics 2026

## About

This repository documents my learning journey through **Summer Analytics 2026**, organized by the **Consulting & Analytics Club, IIT Guwahati**.

The program focuses on building strong foundations in Data Science, Machine Learning, Python programming, data analysis, and visualization through hands-on exercises and projects.

---

## Week 1 Progress

### Day 0 – Environment Setup

Topics Covered:

* Introduction to Summer Analytics 2026
* Setting up the Data Science environment
* Installing and configuring Anaconda
* Working with Jupyter Notebooks
* Introduction to Google Colab
* Introduction to Kaggle

Skills Gained:

* Data science workflow setup
* Cloud-based notebook environments
* Managing Python packages and dependencies

